»CL0:               LIGHTING
»CL1:--------------------------------------

Another  problem  with  »CL6:Alien 2»CL1: is the
poor »CL0:colour scheme»CL1:.  It doesn't really
reflect  any »CL0: atmosphere»CL1:.  But this is
more  in  the  »CL0:2D »CL1: design  department,
