And there are no»CL0: shadows»CL1:.  Shadows are
SO  important.   They don't have to be
»CL0:real»CL1:,  and  all  the  characters don't
need  to cast shadows on all the »CL0:walls»CL1:



    »PIC:dafreak-ec3.iff»
















and »CL0:floors»CL1:, but you could do some »CL0:fake»CL1:
lighting on the surroundings anyway to
